The Xtra Factor NZ - Season 1, Episode 1




Hosted by Guy, Sharyn and Clint from Edge Afternoons, The Xtra Factor will air on FOUR on Sundays and Mondays directly after The X Factor NZ screens on TV3. It will be a play-by-play wrap up of that night's X Factor NZ LIVE episode. It will dissect the drama and reactions to all the action, interviewing judges, contestants and guest performers.




Original Air Date: 15-Mar-2015
